Q1 (A) – Short Answers

a) ip link set eth0 up command-
It enables (activates) the network interface eth0.
Basically turns the interface ON so it can send/receive data.

b) Detect hidden Wi-Fi networks-
Use tools like:
iw dev
iwlist scan
Wireshark / Kismet
Hidden networks still broadcast signals; only SSID is hidden.

c) Configure router interface with IP-
